Explain what this function does, in plain English:

```typescript
function debounce<T extends (...args: unknown[]) => void>(fn: T, ms: number): T {
  let timer: ReturnType<typeof setTimeout>;
  return ((...args: Parameters<T>) => {
    clearTimeout(timer);
    timer = setTimeout(() => fn(...args), ms);
  }) as T;
}
```

